metadata.name: CakeBit
metadata.description:
The rabbit represents absolute love. It looks very cute and friendly, so I would like to give it to someone as a birthday present.
Also, I'm the one who likes to eat desserts as well, so I want to pass on the deliciousness and every good thing that I put into this cake to someone, and it turns out into this picture!

1280 x 1280 px, jpg
